OL,5, Hundreds of sub-postmasters convicted  
OL,6, in the Post Office Horizon scandal     
OL,7, should be able to submit a mass appeal,
OL,8, a former cabinet minister has said.    
OL,10,FSir David Davis, who is seeking to     
OL,11,Fquestion ministers about the issue,    
OL,12,Ftold the BBC there was "no real reason"
OL,13,Fwhy there could not be a "mass case".  
OL,15,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer has also
OL,16,Fsaid all cases need to be revisited.   
OL,18,FIt comes as ministers met on Monday to 
OL,19,Fconsider ways of clearing the names of 
OL,20,Fhundreds of sub-postmasters.           
